         GenomicFeatures, GenomeInfoDb, GenomeInfoDbData, Sushi, moments,
         DT, yaml, AnnotationHub, BSgenome, httpuv, mirbase.db, ggplot2, 
         ggrepel, shinydashboard, shinyjs, organism.dply
